    <p>Mi Codex's libraries can easily be searched and sorted in a variety of ways, making getting the information you need easier.  Your libraries information is secure and safe.  </p>
    <p class="text-center"><%= link_to "Sign up now!", signup_path, class: "btn btn-primary" %></p>
  </div>

</div>
